title: Panasonic 3-Blade Wet/Dry Shaver, ES-SL33 (English)
description: Three precision blades cut close to the roots of your beard for an ultra-close shave. The 30° nano-polished sharp-edged inner blades make quick work of tough hairs for outstandingly smooth results. Round-shaped outer foils follow the contours of your face for efficient coverage and maximum comfort. The water shutters allow you to easily clean the head by simply rinsing it under running water.
